<template>
  <n-result status="404" title="404 服务器娘受不了跑路了哦" description="你们这样压榨是不人道的">
    <template #footer>
      <n-button type="primary" @click="handleClick">听个歌转换一下心情吧</n-button>
    </template>
  </n-result>
</template>

<script>
import { defineComponent } from "vue";

export default defineComponent({
  setup() {
    function handleClick() {
      window.open("https://res.kcn3388.club/404.html", "_blank");
    }
    return {
      handleClick,
    };
  }
});
</script>
